{"tid":1346800,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"琴日係恐怖襲擊","createTime":"2019-07-22T04:52:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T07:38:08.000Z","uid":242805,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"148f1b04c8eb402a09a8dfa88ebd8c5cdc24a954","tid":1346800,"uid":242805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:52:11.000Z","msg":"對於今次有人係公共交通工具發動無差別襲擊公民事件，由於係針對該團體以外既所有香港公民，而且係各區有蔓延趨勢，所以我以香港公民既身份，懇請所有人將琴日既攻擊定義為恐怖襲擊。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不可避免地以政治為目的或動機<br />\n訴諸暴力或揚言要訴諸暴力<br />\n<br />\n計劃要對目標或受害人以外的人物或團體造成深遠的心理影響<br />\n<br />\n由具備可被識別的指揮系統及隱蔽細胞系統的組織指揮行動，其成員穿着制服或佩戴可被識別的徽章<br />\n<br />\n由亞國家組織或非國家行為者干犯</span></span></div>"},{"pid":"3c5cd52b48eac6d9324f8bba0663c6f0ad74f6a4","tid":1346800,"uid":94819,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:52:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9d7d992075032f7d1da0d814042a7f17ac5882f5","tid":1346800,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:29:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">跟返自己生日月份，睇返搵邊個講元朗既事</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>【一月、二月】 David R. Stilwell</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.state.gov/biographies/david-r-stilwell/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.state.gov%2Fbiographies%2Fdavid-r-stilwell%2F&d=kduom0GX2PoGtXVt5SjzIGrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=0764a5fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.state.gov/biographies/david-r-stilwell/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>【三月】 Mitch McConnell</strong><br />\nEmail：senator@mcconnell.senate.gov<br />\nTwitter：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/mcconnellpress\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmcconnellpress&d=kduom0GX2PoGtXVt5SjzIGrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=9d5f054d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/mcconnellpress</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>【四月】 Nancy Patricia Pelosi<